name: Knockout City: Season 7 - Mutant Mutiny
storyline: Deep under the streets of Knockout City, a new kind of brawler is bubbling to the surface. What started as a rumor of glowing eyes, squishy footsteps, and muffled snarls from sewer grates is growing into a revolution of massive proportions. The Mutant Mutiny is here for justice!
